Optical measurements were performed with the Perkin-Elmer double-beam spectrophotometer Lambda 19. The spectra of transmission coefficient and reflection coefficient were recorded within the wavelength range from 250 nm to 2000 nm with a step of 1 nm. The optical band gap of the deposited oxides was determined by the model given by formula (1):1αhvm=Ahv-Eg\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
