				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ \Delta E = \left( {KE_{0} - E_{l,t} } \right) = \left[ {\overline{\varepsilon }} \right]Nt $$\end{document}
where N is the film density and ε¯\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
