				\begin{document}$$\overline{\varepsilon }$$\end{document} is the stopping cross section (-factor).

The relationship between the film thickness and the total number of counts of the signal A0 is [33] given as follows:4A0=σE0ΩQNt/cosθ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
